MOË T & CHANDON_CHAMPAGNE_DINNER_AT_LEVEL 23 SIGNATURE
Level 23 Signature_Restaurant is honored to present an exclusive Mo ë t & Chandon_Champagne dinner for one night only on Friday , November 20 . Connoisseurs are invited to experience some of the finest Mo ë t & Chandon champagnes paired with an exquisite five course menu created by Guest_Chef_Cammarata from Le_Méridien_Suvarnabhumi , Bangkok_Golf_Resort & Spa .
Dine on pearch , ricotta and bell pepper tian ( paired with Champagne_Mo ë t Impérial ) , lobster tortelli , cauliflower and asparagus cous cous ( paired with Champagne_Mo ë t Rosé ) , tournedos of veal with torched Balsamic duck liver ( paired with Champagne_Grand_Vintage 2004 - 2006 ) and be entertained by live musical performances and spectacular city views .
